                     <interp inst="t18341205-240-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18341205-cd-36" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18341205-240-offence-1 t18341205-cd-36"></join>26th of November</rs>, 1 pencil-case, value 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 3 snuff-boxes, value 20<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; and 1 convex glass, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18341205-name-305" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18341205-name-305" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
